As many of you know, for optimized searching of a string in a list of strings we use Tries.
Tries take some time to build but then all the searches are much faster.
Here is the time for sol with and w/o tries -
* Without trie ( str in list )-
	O(n*k) where n is length of list and k is length of the string

* With trie ( Trie.checkWord(str) )-
	O(n*k) for building trie
	O(k) for querying
