# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
*We take a list . Add all possible max elements for the current window in a list. and get the answer from it. Each time we add a new element into the list , we remove all smaller elements than that new element from the list .*
 ***PROPER EXPLANATION WITH CODE IS GIVEN BELOW:***
*use sliding window:*

# Complexity
