So first we insert k indexes  and during that we check if element at deque's back is smaller than the next element if its we remove one element from back. And if window size exceeds k we remove from front and at every iteration if i>k-1 we should push front of deque in a vector because front  will be the max in the window size of k .Because we have compared each element from back if its higher we remove if not it will be automatically the max . 
